76
00:04:20,086 --> 00:04:22,687
and most importantly, clean up their shit.

77
00:04:25,195 --> 00:04:31,936
In gameplay, it's a crossover between a roguelike dungeon crawler and a farm management sim.

78
00:04:32,476 --> 00:04:37,297
It's kind of like a messed up Animal Crossing, but more realistic because you can't buy a house.

79
00:04:40,098 --> 00:04:45,179
We launched on PC, Switch, PlayStation, and Xbox last August, and I started working with

80
00:04:45,219 --> 00:04:46,939
the team one month before launch.

81
00:04:47,819 --> 00:04:49,520
The game is published by Devolver Digital.

82
00:04:51,114 --> 00:04:55,159
