96
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:50,901
alongside the PC versions of games like Persona 4,

97
00:05:51,021 --> 00:05:53,462
God of War, Spider-Man, Final Fantasy VII Remake.

98
00:05:53,983 --> 00:05:56,744
But really, all of that, that did not come from nowhere.

99
