203
00:11:26,886 --> 00:11:28,828
whether that's the brand name, whether it's

204
00:11:28,868 --> 00:11:30,369
the community of players, whether it's

205
00:11:30,389 --> 00:11:32,271
their friends that play with that specific game,

206
00:11:32,331 --> 00:11:34,818
whether it's familiarity, because things actually don't change.

207
00:11:35,314 --> 00:11:37,215
And all of these are ways that you can stand out.

208
00:11:39,392 --> 00:11:42,173
So back to the question, does social media convert?

