00:22:20,776 --> 00:22:25,921
Also, it kind of plays with expectations where if you think of a cult sacrifice,

413
00:22:25,941 --> 00:22:29,204
you might think of someone at an altar in a robe and like with a dagger.

414
00:22:29,484 --> 00:22:31,666
But nah, let's take this up several levels.

