00:22:31,706 --> 00:22:33,848
We've got this tentacle monster coming out of the ground.

416
00:22:34,229 --> 00:22:35,350
That is the trailer moment.

417
00:22:35,650 --> 00:22:37,831
And a trailer moment is good because, well, they were thinking,

418
00:22:37,891 --> 00:22:40,893
how can we put this in a trailer so then it would look good there?

419
00:22:41,433 --> 00:22:43,274
And then that also applies to social media.

420
00:22:43,515 --> 00:22:45,236
It's something that within just a few seconds,

421
00:22:45,296 --> 00:22:47,777
it catches attention and teaches something about this game.

422
00:22:48,137 --> 00:22:51,659
Also, you can see that there's a cute animal, which everyone loves cute animals.

423
00:22:52,620 --> 00:22:54,983
Next, we have support the fantasy.

424
00:22:55,263 --> 00:22:57,046
So this is another thing that the guys thought about.

425
00:22:57,847 --> 00:22:59,729
They started brainstorming different mechanics

426
00:22:59,769 --> 00:23:01,351
to add on top of the gameplay loop.

427
00:23:01,972 --> 00:23:03,754
And they were trying to support the fantasy

428
00:23:03,894 --> 00:23:06,538
of start your own cult of cute animals.

429
00:23:06,658 --> 00:23:08,661
So always going back to that fantasy

430
00:23:08,721 --> 00:23:09,802
and that forward pitch.

431
00:23:11,017 --> 00:23:13,012
And anything that didn't support that fantasy,

432
00:23:13,012 --> 00:23:16,121
it was cut as soon as they realized that it didn't.

433
00:23:16,581 --> 00:23:19,143
So James was watching John Wick one day,

434
00:23:19,583 --> 00:23:23,206
and he realized in John Wick that everything in that world is around assassins.

435
00:23:23,507 --> 00:23:26,569
Keanu Reeves is an assassin, all the people he fights are assassins,

436
00:23:26,869 --> 00:23:29,291
like the whole world building is all around assassins.

437
00:23:29,651 --> 00:23:32,394
And that's where they started to build a world around cults.

438
00:23:32,834 --> 00:23:36,937
The bosses are bishops, the enemies are other cultists,

439
00:23:37,097 --> 00:23:39,559
there's religious imagery like everywhere in the game.

440
00:23:40,632 --> 00:23:45,813
Even something like the lamb is a religious connotation to connect to this world of cults.

441
00:23:47,054 --> 00:23:49,554
And I love this animation that James made.

442
00:23:49,814 --> 00:23:55,196
This is for one of the bosses, this boss transformation where you get to see a bishop

443
00:23:55,256 --> 00:23:58,957
is someone who you might expect to be kind of conservative, dressed in these robes, and

444
00:23:58,977 --> 00:24:04,098
then it becomes this huge, crazy, scary monster, and each of the bishop bosses do this.

445
00:24:07,359 --> 00:24:08,079
So on Twitter...

446
00:24:09,067 --> 00:24:11,772
If you've grabbed their attention at least enough to stop scrolling,

447
00:24:12,093 --> 00:24:14,134
then now can you convert it to information

