00:24:45,082 --> 00:24:46,963
So both of these things, now we're not just...

458
00:24:47,523 --> 00:24:51,090
We're not just provoking someone, we're not just instigating a funny initial reaction,

459
00:24:51,350 --> 00:24:55,398
but we're also trying to teach someone about this unique mechanic that our game has that

460
00:24:55,438 --> 00:24:56,981
makes it stand out to other games.

461
00:24:58,464 --> 00:24:59,145
And on TikTok...

462
00:25:00,276 --> 00:25:02,878
So when we're thinking about converting someone's attention,

463
00:25:03,299 --> 00:25:06,461
sometimes it might be, the end goal might be different

464
00:25:06,501 --> 00:25:08,203
depending on whatever platform you're on.

465
00:25:08,623 --> 00:25:10,324
On a discovery platform like TikTok,

466
00:25:10,605 --> 00:25:12,226
so a place where your primary goal

467
00:25:12,306 --> 00:25:14,368
is to tell new people about the game,

468
00:25:14,848 --> 00:25:18,051
then my goal is to get that content

469
00:25:18,091 --> 00:25:20,233
into as many people's eyes as possible.

470
00:25:21,133 --> 00:25:22,615
So how does TikTok work?

471
00:25:23,035 --> 00:25:24,576
How does it show new content to people?

472
00:25:25,858 --> 00:25:27,499
Videos show up in your For You page.

473
00:25:27,839 --> 00:25:32,302
You can do po- and when, let's say I'm watching and something shows up, I can do

474
00:25:32,402 --> 00:25:34,103
a positive or a negative engagement.

475
00:25:34,203 --> 00:25:39,185
Positive engagements are things like likes, favorites, shares, comments, or

476
00:25:39,225 --> 00:25:40,506
just watching the whole thing through.

477
00:25:40,786 --> 00:25:44,228
And then negative engagements are swiping away before the video is done.

478
00:25:44,488 --> 00:25:48,850
And you can also, uh, like hold tap and say that you don't like videos like this.

479
00:25:49,390 --> 00:25:51,831
And then the For You page will populate with videos that

480
00:25:51,871 --> 00:25:53,252
match your positive engagements.

481
00:25:53,572 --> 00:25:58,459
So let's say I'm really into dogs and I really want to watch only dog videos.

482
00:25:58,759 --> 00:26:01,182
So I'll open TikTok, a video will show up.

483
00:26:01,402 --> 00:26:03,125
